lead_paragraph: As many of you know, constructor Joon Pahk has been playing his heart out on Jeopardy. If you missed the original airing and would like to see what transpired, Nancy Shack, puzzledom's de facto photographer and videographer, has graciously uploaded the videos to YouTube, and you can watch them here.
